Package: deremotelauncher
Depends: libdelauncher1, libdragengine1, libgl1, libx11-6, ${misc:Depends}
Architecture: amd64
Description: Drag[en]gine Remote Launcher
 Allows launching Drag[en]gine based games on another platform.
 .
 This can be used for testing games on another platform without
 the need to install the IGDE nor checking out the game development
 repository on this platform. Simply run the remote launcher and
 connect to a platform running the IGDE. Then synchronize when
 changes are done and run. Logs are transmitted back to the IGDE.
